# Scrabble Showdown ðŸŸ¨

A simple two-player Scrabble-style game built in Python. Designed for classroom pair programming.

## How to Play
1. Run `main.py`
2. Get a random set of letters
3. Enter a word using those letters
4. Game scores your word using Scrabble rules

## Features
- Word validation (basic)
- Scrabble scoring system
- Custom letter draws
- Player reflection journal

## Requirements
- Python 3.8+
- Works in terminal

## Authors
This game was built in pairs! See `journal.md` for team contributions.
